value:
A festival for fighters, eh? Seems like
there's a festival for everything! So...
how 'bout one for dragons?

Y'know, I remember princey dropping
by an arena when he needed cash...
Well, no danger of dyin' this time!

I wonder if Kris would want to crack
some skulls. Our powers combined,
we'd sweep the competition!

Mirages are pretty common in the
desert, right? They trick you into
seeing things...just like me!

Y'know, I bet if I impersonated a
dancer, I'd get everyone on their
feet in no time! But who to choose...

How'd I get past your guards? Easy!
I just went ahead and impersonated
$Nf. Hah!

Yeah! This is the best feelin' in the
world! Keep it up, keep it up!

Hah hah! Life's too short not to laugh
at yourself! Feelin' less nervous now?
Good. No point bein' too serious.

Dang! I knew somethin' was off. My
transformation must've failed partway
through...

Everyone's spirits are soarin' at this
festival. And with this, mine are too!

The name's Xane. So, these are the
festival grounds? Who should I mimic
first to make the biggest splash?

Funny story: Nailah caught me right
as I started to impersonate her. The
wolf queen herself, outta nowhere.$k$pThought I was done for, but she just
chuckled and said I didn't look nearly
fierce enough for her liking...$k$pGuess even royals like her gotta have
a sense of humor. We both had a
good laugh over that one.$k$pEven though we're here to celebrate
the land's seasons and culture, we
gotta have fun while doing it too.$k$pIf I can help just one person forget
their troubles for a day, I'm gonna
keep at it till I collapse!
えいっ
どうだい？
ひゃっ…
ちっきしょう…
Not today!
Wanna dance?
Let me show you!
You're not getting away!
They got me, dammit...
ん？
Up and at 'em!
Get back out there!
This festival's a little on the rowdy side!
Hey, what was that? You lookin' for a fight? This seems to be the place! *chuckle*
Maybe I should change into someone with BIG muscles. I could muscle my way to the top of the heap!
Does it even matter who wins? But I guess I can't just watch, now can I?
Imagine if I changed into you and took the crown! Ain't gonna happen, but you'd be tickled, wouldn't you?
Sure.
Y'know...
Let's see here...
